1. Danas *padaju* jake kiše. (Today strong rains are falling.)
2. Ne znam zašto mi *padaju* ruke. (I don't know why my hands are becoming weak.)
3. Oni *padaju* u ljubav na prvi pogled. (They fall in love at first sight.)
4. Svakog dana *padaju* cene akcija. (Every day stock prices are falling.)
5. Kada *padaju* temperature, ljudi se oblače deblje. (When temperatures drop, people wear thicker clothes.)
6. Često mi *padaju* na pamet stvari koje sam mogao bolje uraditi. (I often think about things I could have done better.)
7. Nekim ljudima *padaju* na pamet najbolje ideje u najneočekivanijim situacijama. (Some people get the best ideas in the most unexpected situations.)
8. U ovo doba godine *padaju* opale lišća. (In this time of year, leaves are falling.)
9. Kada *padne* noć, grad postaje drugačije mesto. (When night falls, the city becomes a different place.)
10. Nadam se da mi neće *pasti* na pamet da odustanem. (I hope I won't think about giving up.)